Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:35.30,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Be careful out there, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:37.99,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.57,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:46.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.86,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It looks like the one Menma used to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.92,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.65,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.26,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Do I {\i1}look{\i0} okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.07,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Take a good look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.72,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.46,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Please. Let them work this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:24.60,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:29.93,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,This is the perfect chance. If he doesn't take advantage of it, there may not be another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:31.17,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Tsuruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:41.46,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey, I look like Menma, right? I do, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.48,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Don't I look like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.01,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yukiats—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.42,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Can't you see her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.29,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:53.77,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's my fault Menma died that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.32,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? It couldn't possibly be your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,If anything, it was my—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.16,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:04.64,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,If I hadn't that to Menma, she wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.08,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I made her die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:15.10,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,If Menma were to reappear to anyone, it should be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.81,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,To haunt or to curse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.85,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Either way, it should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,But she never showed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.60,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.18,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:37.33,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That's how I know she doesn't exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.83,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,She doesn't exist anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.16,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.73,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma says she's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.33,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're still saying that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:07.64,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She says thank you for the hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.20,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And that she's sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:20.06,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Look, I don't really understand it myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.59,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.31,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.34,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.53,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Are you sure we should let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.35,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,It itches...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.43,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Well, I'm done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.53,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Did you already know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.65,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You could say I caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:00.34,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,He'd been asking me to hang out with him after school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:05.09,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,He'd pretend he was buying presents for his inexistent girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:12.86,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It was women's clothing. A white one-piece dress with a ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.68,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Should we really have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.67,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yeah. I figure you should squeeze all the pus out of a wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:29.15,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,But because he's rotten to the core, if you squeeze it all out, then there might not be anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.85,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:43.95,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,"Thanks for the hairpin... And, I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.12,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.34,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Wait up, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.50,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.55,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.23,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hold on, Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.80,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Why? I can't! Jintan's gonna—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.32,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Just let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:17.04,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're not ugly at all, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:18.98,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.69,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I thought it would suit you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.11,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I thought so because I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:41.45,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Jintan is gonna get away, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.82,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,So I have to go chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.80,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,We'll talk about this later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.27,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Maybe it doesn't go well with my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.26,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Now I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:44.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, Me—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.43,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.30,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Do you want something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.15,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.87,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I want Ken-chan Ramen!	{Ken-chan is a brand name}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.95,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.96,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And you can't find it anywhere nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.77,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.45,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.26,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'll go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.35,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You don't have to; anything else you have is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.23,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.74,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma died,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.35,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,but now, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.75,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She came to me, not Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:35.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I didn't care whether she was a ghost or a hallucination,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.58,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,but I avoided thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:45.82,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It's fun when we're all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.91,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It's fun being with Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:54.80,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's why I felt that it's okay not to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:09:00.58,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why is Menma here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.98,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,You're way too popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:33.15,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,They didn't have Ken-chan Ramen. So, instead, I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:35.79,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You got all of this instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.99,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.30,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and sit down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.98,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:53.40,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,About what? Anyway, the popsicle is going to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.45,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I want you to grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why bring that up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.09,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm doing the best I can, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.98,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,In a lot of ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:11.77,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And, of course, I haven't been as obsessed as Yukiatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:15.41,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,but in my own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.24,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.45,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I have a lot of things going on, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.13,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I don't have the time to babysit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:27.71,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.24,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.79,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, man, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.65,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,What's all this? Are you having a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.25,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Is that a popsicle? How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Mind if I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.90,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,That's not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.12,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.64,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What did I mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.84,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What do I have going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.82,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I eat, browse the web,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.50,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,sleep, play videogames,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,sleep, and then eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.14,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I just repeat that cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.85,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.94,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.59,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,So, I'll take the train on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:24.57,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'll be done with work at around 7, so after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.74,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Gee, it's great that you decided to tag along, Naruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:31.48,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.97,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I was counting on you being there when I made plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:38.11,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,so I was pretty worried when you told me you wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:42.18,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,That's right. Ryou would be pissed at you, otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.84,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Ryou has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.30,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Hey, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:50.12,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You've been really unsociable lately, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:53.63,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,We were even wondering if you still wanted to be friends or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.67,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Geez, Haruna. Your jokes are too harsh. Don't you think so, Naruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,{Yukiatsu speaks decent English}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:24.27,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Damn. The next one doesn't come for another 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.00,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.40,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,In fact, it's creepy how much you haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.62,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,How do you want me to act, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.28,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:48.24,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Do you want me taunt you can call you a femboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:54.00,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. I might prefer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.80,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you didn't try to use me to restore balance to your self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:05.01,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I managed to put an end to a few things. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:14.20,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,So then he texts me, saying he loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.68,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,For real? Sounds like a dream come true. {riajuu = slang; something like 'living the dream' as used on 4chan}  {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.81,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,She got a train and rode it all the way to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.75,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,And she's lugging around a huge shopping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.71,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It's a costume. You'd know all about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.33,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:34.75,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,There are certain things you can't manage unless you change your costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.00,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You were great! Awesome! Awesome! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:55.16,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,Stick the next one in, Ryou. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.43,Default,Ryou,0,0,0,,Don't talk like a slutty schoolgirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:01.76,Default,Girl2,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is, just hurry up, Ryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.97,Default,Ryou,0,0,0,,What you gonna do schoolgirl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:02.98,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.55,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Calm down, Haruna! {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You look like you're forcing yourself to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.60,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I'm not forcing myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,{fuck their gibberish in the background}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.56,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.62,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sorry, guys. Naruko and I are gonna call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.26,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:23.85,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I think she's not feeling well, and I have to get up early tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I gotta catch One Piece, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.42,Default,Ryou,0,0,0,,Doesn't One Piece air the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.51,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.82,Default,Ryou,0,0,0,,You guys are no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.60,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Tell all about it later, Naruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.04,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.26,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.72,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.22,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Is the train station really this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:54.01,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I thought we'd just walk to the station together...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:58.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. That's not what "get out of here" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:03.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,And I'm a bit buzzed, so I wanna "rest" for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.00,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I-I'm really not feeling well, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you get some rest, too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.95,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,You're talking about a different kind of rest, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.92,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! What about One Piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,One Piece airs the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.49,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,What? Why don't you just go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be a waste though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.21,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,They're black aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.86,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Wai— Get off of me! I said I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.15,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.90,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,No, not, "Yeah, sure."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.37,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Let me go! {how did everyone in gg predict EVERYTHING that would happen in this show?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.28,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Let me go you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.19,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that you, Anjou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:48.55,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm hanging out with Yadomi right now. You want in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.54,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! I found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:57.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,This is such bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.64,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I just rescued a girl from the arms of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:18.40,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That was the most clichéd thing I've ever done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.62,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,You call that a rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:23.29,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Wouldn't a rescue involve throwing a punch or two and tearing me away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:27.80,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm hot and I'm smart, but unfortunately I'm a bit lacking in the strength department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.96,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:32.71,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That aside, you're gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.37,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I don't want to be told that by a tranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.15,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:44.31,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I thought so. Hearing that makes it easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.37,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Are you a virgin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:53.52,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong with that? {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.66,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Wanna go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.18,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Don't you like Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.12,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:10.41,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I... can't. I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.43,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.22,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is it Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:15.34,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What do you see in that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.10,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,What do I see in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:20.01,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Don't act like you've figured it out! I never said I liked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.98,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,He was a leader, smart, and athletic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.14,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,But that was all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:31.20,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,That's true, but he's kind in unexpected ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:36.86,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,And I think if he fixed his hair, he'd look a bit like Yama from Hey! Say! JUMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.01,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I don't even know if I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:51.27,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I just can't stop thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.86,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Thinking about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.75,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Menma died, then his mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:03.11,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,It became tough to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:07.82,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,I was actually a bit happy that we'd be going to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:12.84,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,But Yadomi can't forget about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:18.84,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You can't forget the Yadomi that can't forget about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.40,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.14,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:26.07,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,Back then you said Yadomi's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.09,Default,Naru,0,0,0,,You said you'd been hanging out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.92,Default,Ann,0,0,0,,We're letting an express train pass. Please wait for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.55,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,We've been left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.45,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.50,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Ding-dong. {Poppo makes the sound of a temple bell being rung here}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.21,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.24,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,So why are you eating at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.64,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Didn't I bring you some wild plants in exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.69,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Tempura was the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.36,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,He looks like he's really enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.93,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You've got dirt above your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.90,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Is Menma here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.61,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.05,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma should eat some tempura too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:43.68,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Do you seriously believe in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.33,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Didn't I already say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.30,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.91,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I've thought it over once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:52.72,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:58.05,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about this, but Menma being here probably isn't a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.81,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,It means she couldn't go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.51,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,So that must be why she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.95,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Go to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:13.42,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I don't know. I just don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.14,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.41,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.53,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Is Menma over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.14,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.57,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Alrighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.68,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:26.15,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Hey Menma, how about giving us a little hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.83,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I'll grant it quicker than you can ring a bell. {I actually think he makes a reference to the custom of ringing a bell at hatsumode to make a wish}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.62,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,There's something you want right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.43,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,You can rely on me a bit, too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.95,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I want to let you go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.74,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, Hisakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:44.12,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Come on, Menma! Please, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:49.10,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,And let me see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.44,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,No good? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.37,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:59.70,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I want to talk with everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:06.96,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But I just don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:06.95,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,How about we all think about it together, Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.42,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I don't know about my wish, or about going to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.48,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I just don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:15.15,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Can't we? Let's think about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.53,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.35,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,And then you can...
