Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:10.24,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Upon pages and pages of entries
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.45,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,We've put down all our emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.70,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,But now I've hit a writer's block
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.66,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to finish this page anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:24.83,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Putting a bookmark in my diary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:29.92,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You and I go out to ride the bike we found in the dumpster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.09,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Let's go to our secret place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.43,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Where we piled up our bricks of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:42.64,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Run up the hill, where we can see the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.23,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Where we can see the sky so fearfully blue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:50.44,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,With cider in my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:54.90,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,My other hand helps me search for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.03,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You used to come find me way back when
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.70,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You used to demand me of so much more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:09.50,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,You're both still standing right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:17.30,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,Yet why do I pray to see you both again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:25.39,Opening 2,,0,0,0,,There must be something off with me
