Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:45.67,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:49.03,Ending,,0,0,0,,The fireworks blossomed heartrendingly beautiful across the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:55.62,Ending,,0,0,0,,and time passed as swiftly as the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,We met in an unexpected moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:37.44,Ending,,0,0,0,,when you called out to me at the crosswalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:40.11,Ending,,0,0,0,,"Let's walk home together."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:02.88,Ending,,0,0,0,,We shared so many happy times and thrilling adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:09.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,together in our secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:17.10,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams we shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:24.19,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we will meet again in another August, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:31.41,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:34.20,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,And I know it must've been painful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:38.46,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:45.67,Ending 2,,0,0,0,,But those are my best memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.73,Title,Yuki,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\pos(80,213)}{\an1}Episode 5 \N\N Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.16,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.71,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Could you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.29,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Please, just let it go.
